Class Alumno

  • java.lang.Object
    • Alumno
  • public class Alumno
extends java.lang.Object
    It is wanted to get the average of grade points of Object Oriented Programming students. For this, the abstract concept "pupil" is modeled. When an instance of Alumno is created, as grade points are not known yet, they are initialized in zero.
